Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on the use of autonomous surface vehicles (ASVs) to automate the process of river surveying, which falls under the domain of robotics. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper may involve computer vision techniques for analyzing the curves of the river to infer the speed of the water current. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper may involve the use of AI techniques for optimizing the coverage of the river based on meanders. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper may involve the use of control systems for guiding the ASVs along the optimal coverage trajectories. 
- cs.GR (Graphics): The paper may involve the visualization of the coverage trajectories on a map or graph.
